			<h2 class="text-[30px] text-center lg:text-left font-heading font-bold tracking-wide leading-8 md:leading-[62.50px] md:text-[50px] text-text-primary ">Specialists in Modern Electrical Solutions</h2>
			<p class="text-base md:text-lg text-center lg:text-left tracking-tight font-montserrat text-text-secondary leading-[33px]">With over 15 years of experience, Switchup Electrical brings cutting-edge expertise to every project. We specialize in EV charger installations, pool and spa electrical, smart home automation, and luxury residential work across Auckland.</p>
			<div class="flex gap-4 pt-3 items-center">
				<CallIcon/>
				<p class="flex flex-col text-text-secondary font-montserrat tracking-tight">
					<span class="text-2xl font-bold leading-9 text-primary-200">0211396512</span>
					<span class="text-lg leading-8">Available 24/7</span>
				</p>
			</div>
			<Button text="Get Free Quote" href="/contact" />
		</div>

		<div>
			<img src="/about-img.png" alt="Switchup Electrical professional electrician" />
		</div>
	</section>

